Package: athletegps
Type: Package
Title: Access STATSports GPS Data via Third-party 'APIs'
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Abdurrahman", "Kikhia",email = "a.kikhia11@gmail.com",role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides helper functions and wrappers to simplify authentication, data retrieval, and result processing from 'STATSports' 'APIs'.
    Designed to streamline integration for practictioners, analysts, and researchers working with GPS data. For further documentation on integrating with 'STATSports' 'APIs', 
    see: <https://elitesupport.statsports.com/hc/en-us/articles/13494019543965-Share-Data>
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/a-kikhia11/athletegps
BugReports: https://github.com/a-kikhia11/athletegps/issues
Imports:
    dplyr,
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    keyring,
    lubridate,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    tidyr
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
